4) Making mass24.dat in ISOTOPES, copy to /home/sergio/SPECTRA/MASS_ISOTOPES (see Readme in that dir)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

AIM :    Get molparams.txt and make mass24.dat, copy to /home/sergio/SPECTRA/MASS_ISOTOPES/mass24.dat

cd ISOTOPES
more Readme

Contents
1) Get the masses
2) get rid of DOS
3) edit molparam.txt so everything is in 5 columns for easy matlab reading
4) check this has been done correctly, using check_mass2X.m
5) then run convert2mass2X.m (was convert2mass20.m)
6) cp /asl/data/hitran/H2024/ISOTOPES/mass24.dat /home/sergio/SPECTRA/MASS_ISOTOPES/mass24.dat
   cp /asl/data/hitran/H2024/ISOTOPES/Readme     /home/sergio/SPECTRA/MASS_ISOTOPES/Readme_mass24

%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%

5) Making vibration functions QTIPS, copy to /home/sergio/SPECTRA/Global_Data_HITRAN2024 ((see Readme in that dir)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

cd QTIPS
more Readme

Contents
1) Download files from hitran website
2) Copy them to /home/sergio/SPECTRA/Global_Data_HITRAN2024/
3) make super-uper program TIPS_2024_try_include1.f
4) make main program that calls TIPS_2024
5) compile main program that calls TIPS_2024
6) Copy the Readme file to UMBC_LBL

TIPS2024 : ifort -o TIPS_2024_allisotopes.x -names uppercase -extend-source 132 -O3 TIPS_2024_allisotopes.f

